&gt;  &gt; 1) SQUARE: use &#39;Ed&#39; + &#39;Roar&#39;. (I&#39;m open to persuasion.)
&gt;  &gt; 2) NEAR: use &#39;Eat&#39; + &#39;Roar&#39;. (I&#39;m open to persuasion.)
